query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 b q1 s t1 tq1 u1) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.score >= 1 AND q1.score <= 10
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('filters',
'multisite',
'office-365')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('diy',
'sharepoint',
'wordpress')
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.name IN ('Commentator',
'Custodian',
'Editor',
'Famous Question',
'Informed',
'Popular Question',
'Revival',
'Scholar',
'Student',
'Teacher',
'Tumbleweed')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 0 AND u1.downvotes <= 10
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
